    <item>
      <title>新兴市场的股票在中国技术增长中达到了三个月的高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/emerging-stocks-rise-to-three-month-high-as-deepseek-lifts-mood</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在腾讯控股有限公司（Tencent Holdings Ltd.）融入DeepSeek的AI模型之后，新兴市场股票周一攀升至三个月的高点，并在中国提高了情绪，并表示北京表示认可私营部门的认可，被认为是恢复经济增长的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/emerging-stocks-rise-to-three-month-high-as-deepseek-lifts-mood</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 04:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>用欧佩克+考虑四月产量远足的延迟的石油稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一个动荡的会议上，欧佩克+考虑将每月供应量增加到4月开始，因此在一个动荡的会议上，石油在每桶售价接近75美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 23:31:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲国防支出提升股票，伤害债券：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/asia-set-for-cautious-open-as-us-eu-tensions-rise-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲债券在国防公司中滑倒，而股票则随着更大的军事支出的可能性而集会，这可能会迫使政府在未来几年内提高借贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/asia-set-for-cautious-open-as-us-eu-tensions-rise-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 22:44:25 GMT</pubDate>
